Reinforcement Learning. 

Explanation: The paper discusses a specific approach to reinforcement learning called "Multigrid Q-Learning." The authors describe how this method can be used to solve problems in which an agent must learn to make decisions based on feedback from its environment. The paper includes a detailed explanation of the Q-Learning algorithm and how it can be extended to work with multiple grids. Overall, the focus of the paper is on using reinforcement learning to solve complex problems, making it a clear example of this sub-category of AI.
